values
  ($q$MMDI-SOP -Production$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-SOP -Production.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ZOvpVa2d2IBp7YzNtjNX_AzdZ11yoJd-/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 46436, $q$MMDI SOP - Production Process (ISO 9001:2015 QMS, Doc No. MMDI-QMS-QSP NO 3, effective 1 April 2024). Purpose: standardized guidelines for large-format printing. Scope: pre-press technicians, printing machine operators, finishing staff, QC personnel. Responsibilities defined for Production Manager, Pre-press Technicians, Printing Machine Operators, Finishing Staff, QC Personnel. Procedure stages: pre-press preparation (file review, print-ready conversion, proofs); pre-printing operations (substrate/fabric verification); printing setup (substrate selection, machine config, nozzle/color calibration); printing process (monitoring, drying, dye-sublimation heat/pressure); finishing operations (trimming, hot-air seaming, eyelets, pocketing, mounting on rigid boards/canvas/aluminium frames); quality control checks; packaging and shipping; maintenance and cleaning; record keeping; continuous improvement; compliance with industry/environmental regulations; emergency procedures; documentation/reporting; periodic SOP review/revision; staff training and development.$q$, now()),
  ($q$MMDI-COMPETENCY MATRIX$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-COMPETENCY MATRIX.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1H1ENviGIzwd2d1hcGIfb8wDEiepuUHm8/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 738613, NULL, now()),
  ($q$MMDI-QMS_QUALITY OBJECTIVES$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-QMS_QUALITY OBJECTIVES.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NITM5zaOGGZiCnaJmtBO6aFRzeiiChQg/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 736295, $q$ISO 9001:2015 QMS Quality Objectives, Doc No. MMDI-QMS-ANNEX 004, effective 1st April 2024, Issue 1 / Version 1.0. Nine objectives with target/responsibility/duration/monitoring: (1) Increase revenue 30% growth YoY, Sales/Marketing, 12 months, monitored by Directors. (2) Achieve 90%+ customer satisfaction, Customer Service, quarterly, Quality Assurance. (3) Maintain 95%+ print quality acceptance rate, Production, monthly, Production Manager. (4) 98%+ on-time delivery rate, Operations, weekly, Operations Manager. (5) Reduce waste/rework 10% annually, Quality Control, Quality Assurance. (6) Enhance employee skills/engagement via biannual surveys and training, HR, HR Manager. (7) Adhere to industry standards/regulations, Compliance, ongoing, Compliance Officer. (8) Continuously improve processes/technology, Process Improvement, quarterly, Operations Manager. (9) Maintain supplier quality/relationships via periodic evaluations, Procurement, semi-annually, Procurement Manager.$q$, now()),
  ($q$MMDI-TRAINING ATTENDANCE SHEET FORMAT-Health and Safety$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-TRAINING ATTENDANCE SHEET FORMAT-Health and Safety.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QU6CfNBZ3k-30X6Hg3eIJXZN4S9CLlxH/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 40814, NULL, now()),
  ($q$MMDI-QMS_FORMAT-Non-confirmity Report$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-QMS_FORMAT-Non-confirmity Report.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mAa1SuJ5CY9Mp2uAftm7Mdp-r2wurAcG/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 38250, NULL, now()),
  ($q$MMDI-QMS_FORMAT-Non-confirmity and Corrective Action Plan$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-QMS_FORMAT-Non-confirmity and Corrective Action Plan.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Fo1saLWIo8x94SnA0LcUYGtaNk8GSX4r/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 42288, NULL, now()),
  ($q$MACRO-SOP-PURCHASE$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MACRO-SOP-PURCHASE.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oPBYxmP47H7ymAhgnR3IjKfX2T3GB_6g/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 743850, $q$MMDI SOP - Purchase Process (ISO 9001:2015 QMS, Doc No. MMDI/QMS/SOP NO.2, effective 1 Sept 2023). Purpose: procedure for purchase of all materials at Macromedia Digital Imaging Pvt Ltd. Covers: outsourcing/supply schedule adherence, rate standardization, comparative statements for quotations, sub-contractor bill checking, bill tracking, quality inspection, supplier base widening. Supplier Master maintenance: approval based on price list, market standing, financial status, OEM/distributor association; periodic performance evaluation and rating (quality, delivery promptness, response, after-sales, commercial terms). Material purchase workflow: BOM/Kitting List receipt, quotation calls, PO release, urgent/cash purchase, rejected material handling. Process parameter standards table: schedule prep within 3 days, new supplier selection within 15 days, PO raising per kitting list, rejection replacement within 2 days, supplier rating done quarterly (target >90 for 80% of suppliers, >70 for 20%), bill passing within 3 days of GRN. Lists quality records maintained (approved supplier list, quotation comparison, PO, purchase control register, GRIR, stock register, etc.) and 4 quality objectives around supplier count, purchase cost reduction, supplier rating improvement, and supply schedule adherence.$q$, now()),
