  ($q$MMDI-QSP3-SALES AND CUSTOMER SUPPORT$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-QSP3-SALES AND CUSTOMER SUPPORT.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WiV6CNfp8Q4eGbtcrdOKr2me5J8-gCyp/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 42090, NULL, now()),
  ($q$MMDI-QSP2-PROCUREMENT$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-QSP2-PROCUREMENT.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rFJu2poWBrBz4oGxAV-P2PJOmpZyuBRQ/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 42501, NULL, now()),
  ($q$MMDI-QSP1-PO AND REVIEW OF CUSTOMER REQUIREMENTS$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-QSP1-PO AND REVIEW OF CUSTOMER REQUIREMENTS.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jU1h6qvkGhMs6kGSRq_MXoaOk7_1e_av/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 737098, $q$MMDI QSP1 - Procedure for Purchase Order and Customer Requirements Review (ISO 9001:2015 QMS, Doc No. MMDI-QMS-QSP NO 1, effective 1 April 2024). Purpose: standard procedure for receipt/review of customer POs. Scope: sales and pre-press teams. Responsibility: Sales Executive, Pre-press Operations Executive. Process steps: order receipt & entry (logged in order management/ERP with full details); document review for completeness/accuracy; customer requirements review (design files, color specs, print size, paper type, finishing) cross-referenced against equipment capability; customer communication for discrepancies; feasibility assessment; quote preparation if scope expands; order confirmation; production planning and resource allocation; quality control during/after production; packaging and shipping per PO delivery terms; documentation and record-keeping of the full order lifecycle; post-delivery customer feedback for continuous improvement.$q$, now()),
  ($q$MMDI-QSP-HR and training process$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI-QSP-HR and training process.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1sUxrFAk3Lw95_vNzakaHGZh5jMkIAljR/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 736665, $q$MMDI HR & Training Process (ISO 9001:2015 QMS, Doc No. MMDI/QMS/QSP NO.3, effective 1 April 2024). Purpose: guidelines for hiring, appointment, training, rewards/recognition, attendance, and other HR activities, covering all employees including short-term contracts. Responsibility: HR Manager. Recruitment: online postings, CV screening, 3-round interview process (HR -> HR Head -> Director), reference checks, offer letter, background verification, joining formalities, Group Insurance. Induction: 2-day program, joining kit (HR Handbook, Diary, ID Card, SOPs, Brochures, RRA), department-head-led induction, post-induction assessment test, ESI/PF compliance, IT account creation, monthly probation review before confirmation. Attendance: office timings communication, late-coming/absence monitoring, geo-tagged attendance for site employees. Training: annual training plan/calendar prepared by HR with Director approval, competence/skill matrix, training records and feedback maintained. Exit Formalities: 1-month notice period, exit interview, asset/ID collection, NOC from all departments, handover documentation, IT access revocation, final settlement, termination procedures per management instruction.$q$, now()),
