  ($q$Vision & Mission Statement$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$Vision & Mission Statement.docx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MAkWGMwEyxHdNSxOSOnq55zD9OOjAAEZ/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document$q$, 38372, NULL, now()),
  ($q$MMDI ISO Trackers for Documents$q$, NULL, '{}', $q$ISO 9001$q$, $q$MMDI ISO Trackers for Documents.xlsx$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/16cTqlYVJnTLuagDczBSf5kB-uA0gbmC2/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet$q$, 12194, $q$MMDI ISO Trackers for Documents -- master status index of the ISO 9001:2015 QMS documentation set. 23 tracked documents with status and responsibility (mostly 'Completed', owner Mr. Srinivas-MMDI or VSR): Quality Manual (ready, to be reviewed/approved), Risk Register, Opportunities Register, Needs and Expectations of Interested Parties, SWOT/PESTEL Analysis, Quality Objectives, SOPs for Sales & Customer Support / Production / Stores / Procurement / HR & Training / Nonconformity & Corrective Action / Planning for Changes / Maintenance (all completed) and Internal Audits / Control of Documents / Release of Products & Dispatch (still 'In process'), Work Instructions for Machine Operators, HR Competency Matrix, HR Training Records, List of Machines, List of Approved Suppliers, Supplier/Vendor Rating. Useful as a table of contents / gap-check for the QMS document set -- 3 SOPs (Internal Audits, Control of Documents, Release of Products & Dispatch) are flagged as still in process and were not found among the ingested Drive files.$q$, now()),
